description: Bake Nug Tezos Bakery: Baking Nuggets of Digital Gold! Mine for XTZ by collecting our Gold Nuggets. Proceeds from sales are held in treasury. Treasury XTZ staking rewards are redistributed to collectors. Proceeds from royalties increase the value locked in treasury. Yield on our NFTs may be higher than traditional XTZ staking. Each edition collected counts as 1 share. To qualify shares must not be listed for sale. Rewards are paid every 3 days starting 10/10/2021. BakeNug.com/gold
